Package arcade.patch.env.component

Class PatchComponentSitesGraph.SiteEdge

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.core.util.Graph.Edge
      • arcade.patch.env.component.PatchComponentSitesGraph.SiteEdge
  • Enclosing class:
    PatchComponentSitesGraph
    public static class PatchComponentSitesGraph.SiteEdge
extends Graph.Edge
    Extension of Graph.Edge for site edges.

    Node tracks additional hemodynamic properties including radius, length, wall thickness, shear stress, circumferential stress, and volumetric flow rate.
